{"tid":517031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掟手榴彈甩手跌腳邊 強國新兵仲唔知......","createTime":"2018-01-02T02:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T09:35:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"39d7aa767b43e2a31007136406a93d95b1e09493","tid":517031,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180102/large/1514853664_8d74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180102%2Flarge%2F1514853664_8d74.jpg&h=5b87975f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恐怖天兵！內地空軍西安飛行學院一名新兵張宇，去年12月初進行手榴彈實彈投擲時，竟然讓已拉開引信的手榴彈滑脫，讓其掉落在地，班長吳彬彬見狀，急忙撲向張宇，將他護在掩體裏，約3秒鐘後，手榴彈距兩人約1米處爆炸，兩人安然無恙！<br />\n<br />\n據《解放軍報》報道，張宇當時因為緊張，右手大量出汗，結果聽到投擲命令時，手榴彈沒丟出去，反而滑落地上，彈了幾次後落入投擲台。張宇還沒有發現手榴彈已脫手，仍按照預定動作彎腰蹲下，吳彬杉見狀急忙飛撲向張宇，將其護在掩體裏，手榴彈隨即便在兩人身旁大約1米處爆炸。<br />\n其他新兵和現場指揮員都被嚇傻了，還好等濃煙散去後，吳彬彬和張宇都站了起身，兩人都沒事。張宇表示，「爆炸發生時班長將我死死地壓在身下，用身體作為第二道掩體護着我，是班長用命救了我。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180102/57654357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180102%2F57654357&d=ZGLzGSuEDofInY%2FLzkwlTC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b52262db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180102%2F57654357&h=7dbbfd1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180102/57654357</a>"},{"pid":"90936b196ead656fbeec678046b3a5f42f8e811c","tid":517031,"uid":2404,"like":243,"dislike":1,"score":242,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:29:34.000Z","msg":"手榴彈距兩人約1米處爆炸，兩人安然無恙！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591c0107201c9939b81f052901bddad3d681495a","tid":51703